OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1772644277
OL,3,CWealden council pulls out of future
OL,4,Clegal action over Crowborough migrant
OL,5,Ccamp
OL,7,FWealden council's leader has confirmed
OL,8,Fthe authority will not join any
OL,9,Ffurther legal action against the use
OL,10,Fof a former army training camp to
OL,11,Fhouse migrants.
OL,13,FThe site in Crowborough, East Sussex
OL,14,Fopened up to asylum seekers at the end
OL,15,Fof January as part of Government plans
OL,16,Fto stop the use of hotels to house
OL,17,Fthem.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
