OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1772644277
OL,3,CWealden council pulls out of future
OL,4,Clegal action over Crowborough migrant
OL,5,Ccamp
OL,7,FThere's been a large amount of
OL,8,Fbacklash to the measures from local
OL,9,Fresidents group Crowborough Shield who
OL,10,Fwent to the High Court to challenge
OL,11,Fthe Home Office's decision to use the
OL,12,Fbarracks.
OL,14,FThe #100,000 community funded legal
OL,15,Fchallenge, which received support from
OL,16,Fthe local council, was rejected on
OL,17,FFriday by a judge who said the group
OL,18,Fhad "jumped the gun" by inputting
OL,19,Ftheir claim in December, before a
OL,20,Ffinal policy to use the camp had been
OL,21,Fclearly determined.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1772644277
OL,3,CWealden council pulls out of future
OL,4,Clegal action over Crowborough migrant
OL,5,Ccamp
OL,7,FWhilst Crowborough Shield is now
OL,8,Ftrying to raise tens of thousands of
OL,9,Fpounds for fresh legal intervention,
OL,10,FWealden's council's leader Rachel
OL,11,FMillward said it is 'morally wrong' to
OL,12,Fraise false hopes that any subsequent
OL,13,FHigh Court challenge will be
OL,14,Fsuccessful.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1772644277
OL,3,CWealden council pulls out of future
OL,4,Clegal action over Crowborough migrant
OL,5,Ccamp
OL,7,FPosting a video on social, the Green
OL,8,Fparty politician said, "We've now
OL,9,Fdecided not to pursue or support any
OL,10,Ffurther legal action. Our barristers
OL,11,Fhave made clear that to continue to
OL,12,Ftake legal action against the Home
OL,13,FOffice wouldn't achieve anything of
OL,14,Freal value.
OL,16,F"This council has always been against
OL,17,Fthe Home Office's plans for this site.
OL,18,FWe took part in Crowborough Shield's
OL,19,Fcourt case and provided supported
OL,20,Fevidence.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1772644277
OL,3,CWealden council pulls out of future
OL,4,Clegal action over Crowborough migrant
OL,5,Ccamp
OL,7,F"The court recognised that it would be
OL,8,Ffutile for us to issue enforcement
OL,9,Faction, such as a stop notice. That's
OL,10,Fbecause it's Crown land, and we're
OL,11,Fonly allowed to take action with the
OL,12,FGovernment's permission, which they've
OL,13,Frefused.
OL,15,FWealden's council's leader Rachel
OL,16,FMillward published the announcement on
OL,17,Fsocial media
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1772644277
OL,3,CWealden council pulls out of future
OL,4,Clegal action over Crowborough migrant
OL,5,Ccamp
OL,7,F"The reality is that whilst we
OL,8,Fdisagree with the Government's plans,
OL,9,Fwe do not have the powers to stop it
OL,10,Fand we don't serve our residents by
OL,11,Fpretending that we can."
OL,13,FLawyers for campaigners had argued
OL,14,Fthat the Home Office acted unlawfully
OL,15,Fby bypassing the standard planning
OL,16,Fsystem, treating the camp as an
OL,17,F"emergency need".
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1772644277
OL,3,CWealden council pulls out of future
OL,4,Clegal action over Crowborough migrant
OL,5,Ccamp
OL,7,FThey claimed there hadn't been an
OL,8,Fadequate consultation and a lack of
OL,9,Fimpact assessment over the suitability
OL,10,Fof the army camp.
OL,12,FWhilst the judge has opened the door
OL,13,Ffor another attempt Ms Millward said
OL,14,Fany future grounds raised for
OL,15,Fobjection could be rectified by the
OL,16,FHome Office.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1772644277
OL,3,CWealden council pulls out of future
OL,4,Clegal action over Crowborough migrant
OL,5,Ccamp
OL,7,FShe said, "The judge did say that the
OL,8,Fdecision was open to challenge around
OL,9,Fhabitat and environmental regulations.
OL,10,FBut our lawyers are clear that the
OL,11,Ftactical errors that we've identified
OL,12,Fare easily corrected by the Home
OL,13,FOffice.
OL,15,F"In fact, seeing as they now know what
OL,16,Fwe're thinking, they're probably
OL,17,Fworking on it already. Worse still,
OL,18,Feven if we won, the Government would
OL,19,Fbe allowed to retake its decision and
OL,20,Fstart the 12 month clock again, so the
OL,21,Fcamp would be open for even longer."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1772644277
OL,3,CWealden council pulls out of future
OL,4,Clegal action over Crowborough migrant
OL,5,Ccamp
OL,7,F"We must all now turn our attention to
OL,8,Fmaking sure that everyone feels safe
OL,9,Fand secure, and that this works as
OL,10,Fwell as possible. And we will continue
OL,11,Fto press the Home Office to do their
OL,12,Fjob properly and to engage better with
OL,13,Fus all."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
